author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Tile floor protection tips…I use Ram Board to protect new tile floors. I normally tape it to the floor with Frog Tape because that won’t leave a residue on the surface. This is also great on top of tile shower floors and allows me to safely tile the walls while having tools close by 🔥#homerenovation #ramboard #diy #homerepairtutor
title: Tile Floor Protection Tips - #shorts #homerenovation #homerepairtutor
